export const FatBackStudio = () => {

    return <Routes>

        <Route path="*" element={
            // <Authorized>
            <>

                <NavBar />
                <ApplicationViews />
            </>
            // </Authorized>

        } />

        <Route path="/login" element={<Login />} />
        <Route path="/register" element={<Register />} />

        <Route path="reserve" element={
            <Authorized>
                <>
                    <NavBar />
                    <BookingForm />

                </>
            </Authorized>
        } />

        <Route path="myrequest" element={
            <Authorized>
                <>
                    <NavBar />
                    <MyRequest />

                </>
            </Authorized>
        } />

        <Route path="myrequest/:requestId" element={
            <Authorized>
                <>
                    <NavBar />
                    <RequestEdit />

                </>
            </Authorized>
        } />

    </Routes>
}
